---
layout: base.njk
title: Ongoing Projects
description: "View Kusten Contractor's portfolio of completed projects in Kenya. Explore our residential, commercial, and institutional construction work."
---

<section class="projects-hero">
  <img data-src="/assets/images/high-view-house-with-garden-keys-blueprint.webp" loading="lazy" alt="symbol of handing over a house" />
  <div class="breadcrumb">
    <span class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/">Home</a></span>
    <span class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/projects" class="active">Ongoing Projects</a></span>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="carousel-wrapper">
  <div class="container carousel-section scroll-animate delay-1" id="completed-projects">
    <h1>Ongoing Projects</h1>
    <p class="projects-p">This is a testament to our integrated process, where thoughtful design, rigorous execution, and seamless leadership converge to create timeless value. Each project embodies a collaborative pursuitâ€”balancing aesthetic vision with structural integrity, sustainable principles, and human experience.</p>
    <p class="portfolio-note"><i class="bi bi-hand-index"></i> Tap image for more views</p>
    <div class="carousel-container scroll-animate delay-1">
      <button class="nav-btn prev-btn"><i class="bi bi-chevron-left"></i></button>
      <div class="carousel scroll-animate delay-1">
        {% for project in collections.projects %}
        <div class="card portfolio-card" data-index="{{ loop.index0 }}" data-project-index="{{ loop.index0 }}" data-gallery="{{ project.data.gallery | dump | escape }}">
          <div class="card-img-container">
            <img src="{{ project.data.image }}" alt="{{ project.data.title }}" class="card-img" loading="lazy">
            {% if project.data.gallery and project.data.gallery.length > 1 %}
            <div class="card-overlay">
              <span class="view-more-text">View Gallery</span>
              <div class="view-gallery-btn">
                <i class="bi bi-images"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3 class="card-title">{{ project.data.title }}</h3>
            {% if project.data.location %}
            <p class="card-desc">{{ project.data.location }}</p>
            {% endif %}
            <p class="card-desc">{{ project.data.description }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <button class="nav-btn next-btn"><i class="bi bi-chevron-right"></i></button>
    </div>
    <div class="indicators"></div>
  </div>
</section>

